.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Fn libbfio_get_version
function is used to retrieve the library version.
.Sh RETURN VALUES
Most of the functions return NULL or \-1 on error, dependent on the return \
type.
For the actual return values see
.In libbfio.h .
.Sh ENVIRONMENT
None
.Sh FILES
None
.Sh NOTES
libbfio can be compiled with wide character support (wchar_t).
.sp
To compile libbfio with wide character support use:
.Ar ./configure --enable-wide-character-type
 or define:
.Ar _UNICODE
 or
.Ar UNICODE
 during compilation.
.sp
.Ar LIBBFIO_WIDE_CHARACTER_TYPE
 in libbfio/features.h can be used to determine if libbfio was compiled with wide character support.
